============================
Keystroke Savings Rate (KSR)
           ki + ks        
KSR = (1 - ------- ) * 100
             kn           
where: 
       ki = actual keystrokes
       ks = keystrokes required to select suggestion
       kn = keystrokes required with no prediction enabled

ks : 5023
kn : 104001
